Peter James ATHERTON, petitioner,
v.
DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA OFFICE OF THE MAYOR, et al. No. 13-5902. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 13, 2014.

Former decision, 134 S.Ct. 478.

Petition for rehearing denied.

The CHIEF JUSTICE and Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
